untouched, in this view of Solway Street from Ridge Drive in Glendale after 
last week's devastating fire. JOSE GALVEZ / Los Angeles Times; Photo, One 
resident hoses down the roof of his house as the flames approach over the hill 
near Avonoak Terrace. MIKE MULLEN / For The Times 
</P>
