<P>
Wild Art 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA070590-0116 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 243104 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
July 5, 1990, Thursday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
View; Part E; Page 1; Column 3; View Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
