SAN GABRIEL VALLEY DIGEST: FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
<P>
City manager's salary -- A digest item in the July 5 San Gabriel Valley section 
incorrectly reported that Monterey Park City Manager Mark Lewis would get a 
salary increase for the 1990-91 fiscal year. The increase was provided for in 
the city's budget but has not been approved by the City Council. 
</P>
