<P>
PET VACCINATIONS OFFERED 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Dogs will be vaccinated against rabies for $3 cash per animal at two city parks 
during the city's annual low-cost anti-rabies clinic tonight. 
</P>
<P>
Dog licenses will also be sold for $8.41 for spayed or neutered animals and for 
