expected to help the giant conglomerate's expansion. A drill team, above, led 
cheers at a company sports festival at Seoul's Olympic Stadium. ; Photo, 
Workers assemble cameras at Samsung Aerospace's Changwon plant. CHI JUNG NAM / 
For The Times; Photo, At the Samsung Group sports festival last year in the 
Olympic Stadium in Seoul, employees used cards to form the image of Chairman 
Lee Kun Hee. ; Photo, New Samsung employees learn to use computer systems at 
