victory. The Irvine Co. reasoned that the amount was far less than the $330 
million Smith was asking; Smith noted it was 31% more than the $114 million 
Bren offered her in 1983. Once the court totes up the interest and decides who 
pays the lawyers, the award is expected to hit at least $250 million. 
</P>
<P>
